<p><img class= "bubbles_left" src="images/bubbles-design-01.svg">With your insights gathered and opportunities defined, you enter the Design phase. In this phase, you start building prototypes and working through design ideas. You won't try to perfect these too soon. Instead, you will prioritize iteration, testing, and making incremental refinements. Build, test and repeat.
